    <div> of different projects aimed at supporting the development of new technologies in the realm of alternative energy , and marketing these technologies globally . Of course , one objective of the initiative is to ensure that Abu Dhabi can retain its share in the global energy market in the medium term , and even increase it in the long term .</div>
