    <div> Sultan Ahmed Al Jaber : It was always the desire and the vision of the late Sheikh Zayed bin Sultan Al Nahyan that Abu Dhabi should be a green city . These trees represent great wealth to us .</div>
    <div> ����������������������������������������������������</div>
