    <div> ��������������������������</div>
    <div> That is another legacy from Sheikh Zayed ’ s clear vision . He firmly believed that , although Abu Dhabi would always have a central role to play in the energy business , it must also stand apart as an environmentally aware nation . That is why the primary purpose of the Masdar Initiative is to seek new ways and means of tapping into clean energy sources . As long-established energy experts , we see the move in this direction simply as a natural and logical step .</div>
    <div> �����������������������������������������������������</div>
    <div> ����������������������</div>
    <div> The people of Abu Dhabi are completely behind it . Our former president firmly anchored in all of us this understanding of ourselves as a leading energy nation with a great environmental conscience .</div>
    <div> ������������������������������������������������������������</div>
    <div> �����������������������������������������������������������������</div>
